  <steps>
    <step order="0" name="Context Check + Rigor Declaration">
      Output: "🔒 RIGOR LEVEL: FULL — production class deletion + cross-cutting refactor".
    </step>
    <step order="1" name="Review Progress">
      Verify 022 ✅. Update `current-task.md`.
    </step>
    <step order="2" name="Gather Resources + Inventory References">
      Read inputs + knowledge. Grep ALL references to `InvokeSummarizePlaybookTool` + `InvokeInsightsQueryTool` (production + test code). Capture baseline publish size.
    </step>
    <step order="3" name="Refactor Callers">
      For each reference, update to use generic `invoke_playbook` tool path. For the insights path, dispatch goes through `InsightsIntentClassifier` first (unchanged); when classifier returns "playbook" route, invoke `invoke_playbook` with the appropriate playbookId.
    </step>
    <step order="4" name="Delete Bridge Classes">
      Delete `InvokeSummarizePlaybookTool.cs` + `InvokeInsightsQueryTool.cs`. Remove their DI registrations from `AnalysisServicesModule`.
    </step>
    <step order="5" name="Update Tests">
      Update unit tests that referenced deleted classes; replace with tests for generic-path dispatch.
    </step>
    <step order="6" name="Regression Test /summarize + Insights Query">
      Run regression tests for /summarize chat path + insights query chat path. Both MUST pass.
    </step>
    <step order="7" name="Build + Verify Publish Size + Acceptance Criteria">
      `dotnet build` → 0 errors. `dotnet publish -c Release` → delta vs baseline (net negative expected). Walk each criterion.
    </step>
    <step order="9.5" name="Quality Gates (FULL rigor)">
      Run `code-review` + `adr-check`. Verify ADR-010 / ADR-013 / ADR-015 / ADR-018 / ADR-029 + NFR-13 + FR-24 compliance. Both gates MUST pass.
    </step>
    <step order="10" name="Document + Complete">
      Update task POML status complete. TASK-INDEX 023 ✅. Reset `current-task.md`. Report. Pillar 3 closeout note.
    </step>
  </steps>

  <tools>
